SVO Torch is a derived implementation of SVO Pro.

Original SVO authors include Christian Forster, Matia Pizzoli, Zichao Zhang,
Michael Gassner, Manuel Werlberger, Davide Scaramuzza, and contributors at the
Robotics and Perception Group, University of Zurich. The original repository
is distributed under GPLv3. SVO Torch is distributed under GPL-3.0-only; see
LICENSE.

